  <brief_title>Growth Hormone Treatment in Short Children Born Small for Gestational Age</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimization of Growth Hormone Treatment in Short Children Born Small for Gestational Age Based on a Growth Prediction Model-The OPTIMA Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
